snippet.title: Robocop Vs Predator - Free Pc Game Extended Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch, play for FREE and share if you like it! You can find the game in my shop: https://oscarcelestini.itch.io/

A game by Oscar Celestini
Story by Simone Granata
Music by Gianluca Pappalardo
Alternate cover artwork by Piero Trabanelli
